description: In the 70's, great radio stations would blend the very best of popular music of the day. You'd hear Van Morrison, then the Allman Brothers, then Carole King, then Zeppelin. And then, maybe, the Chi-Lites, Marvin Gaye, Gladys Knight or some other great soul artist. Man, oh man, these are great songs!
